title: FC Spicul Fălești
text: FC Spicul Fălești was a Moldovan <a href="association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="F%C4%83le%C5%9Fti">Făleşti</a>, Moldova. The club was founded in 1991 as FC Cristalul Fălești, and was dissolved in 1998. They played 4 seasons in the <a href="Moldovan%20National%20Division">Moldovan National Division</a>, the top division in Moldovan football.
